               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 3ra-91ra)
 I-1) Maṣḥafa
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 3ra-7rb)
 I-2a) Taʾammǝra
                     Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 1 miracle (fols. 7va-8rb)
 I-3) Introductive
                     exhortation and hymn (fols. 9ra-11va)
 I-2b) Taʾammǝra Māryām "Miracles of
                     Mary": 60 miracles (fols. 12ra-90rb)
 I-4) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki ...
                     "I worship Thee ..." (fols. 90rb-91ra)
 II) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus "Miracles of
                     Jesus" (fol. 92ra-120va)
 II-1) ʾƎsaggǝd la-malakotǝka... "I worship Thy
                     Godhead ..." (fols. 92ra-95ra)
 II-2) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus "Miracles of Jesus":
                     18 miracles (fols. 95ra-120va), incomplete
 
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
