                           <item xml:id="a1">
                              <locus target="#2ra">f. 2ra</locus>
                              <desc type="OwnershipNote">Note referring to commissioning or purchase
                                 of the Ms. (?)</desc>
                              <q xml:lang="gez">
                                 <locus target="#2ra">2ra</locus>: ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ [n.l. ኤል]፡ ዘተሣየጥዎ፡
                                 በንዋየ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ወሊቆሙ፡ [n.l.]፡ ወካሕናቱሂ፡ [n.l.]፡ ዘአጽሐፋ፡ ለዘቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡
                                 አበ፡ ጵኵሚስ፡ ትኵኖሙ፡ መድኀኒተ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወነፍስ፡ አመ፡ ይመጽአ፡ በዕለተ፡ ሐዲስ፡ ንጉሠ፡
                                 ነግሥት፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ...</q>
                              <note> The note is written in hand <ref type="hand" target="#h3">c</ref>; some words (names) have been erased. Its content is
                                 not quite clear. The note states that the book has been bought by a
                                 person probably called <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12102TaklaMikael">Takla Mikāʾel</persName> (the same
